    </section>

    <section class="sec3">
        <div class="ctnr">
            <h2>We believe that <b>diverse culture</b> is a requirement for innovation and a <b>better world</b>.</h2>

            <div class="txt">
                <p>At OQVA, we’re not your typical digital agency, we embrace a unique philosophy: every organization exists to provide the individual tools to build their own identity. We design experiences that resonate on a personal level, triggering emotions and sparking conversations. From cutting-edge websites to engaging digital content, our creations are born from a deep understanding of your audience’s deepest desires and aspirations.</p>
    
                <p>With us, you’re getting more than a service — you’re entering a partnership. Together, we’ll build a brand that goes beyond selling, to tell a story, spark a conversation, and foster a community.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec4">

        <picture class="car_marketing" loading="lazy">
            <source srcset="/home/car-mobile.webp" type="image/webp" width="373" height="230" media="(max-width:600px)">
            <source srcset="/home/car-desktop.webp" type="image/webp" width="990" height="611" media="(min-width:600px)">
            <source srcset="/home/car-mobile.png" type="image/png" width="373" height="230" media="(max-width:600px)">
            <source srcset="/home/car-desktop.png" type="image/png" width="990" height="611" media="(min-width:600px)">
            <img src="/home/car.png" alt="car composition" draggable="false" width="373" height="230">
        </picture>

        <h2>We specialise in crafting digital experiences that empower and resonate. Our services include:</h2>

        <div class="services">
            <article>
                <h3>Brand Strategy</h3>
                <p>We delve into the soul of your brand to build strategies that empower your audience, fostering a sense of belonging and collective aspiration.</p>
            </article>
            
            <article>
                <h3>Website Design & Development</h3>
                <p>More than creating visually stunning websites, we design digital platforms that are immersive, interactive, and intimately connected to your brand’s essence.</p>
            </article>
            
            <article>
                <h3>Digital Content Creation</h3>
                <p>Our content isn’t just about conveying information — it's about sparking connections, conversations, and community.</p>
            </article>
        </div>

        <div class="contact">
            <p>Ready to create something meaningful? We’re excited to meet you. Let’s explore the potential of your brand together, uncovering the core essence that will resonate with your audience. Reach out today, and let’s start crafting your unique story.</p>

            <button class="contact_bt" type="button" aria-label="Contact button">Contact us</button>
        </div>

